Question: There are exactly 2 bottles in one image, and exactly 3 in the other.

Reference Answer: False

Right image URL: https://99designs-blog.imgix.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/bottle.jpg?auto=format&q=60&fit=max&w=930

Program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many bottles are in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many bottles are in the image?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} == 2 and {ANSWER1} == 3')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
